{"tid":43463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【NatGeo】首度攝製「深海鬼鯊」影片","createTime":"2016-12-17T13:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T12:58:59.000Z","uid":22675,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e7c7fd5a90a2f122b9af83c0e59cccedd100495b","tid":43463,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T13:46:48.000Z","msg":"National Geographic 製作團隊首次喺深海拍咗段「鬼鯊」（直譯自Ghost Shark，華語地區叫銀鮫，唔少種類嘅銀鮫可以係淺水地區捉到，National Geographic今次拍嘅呢個品種點鼻藍奇美拉，pointed-nose blue chimaera，得深海先有，實際上佢哋唔算係鯊魚）嘅紀錄片。 <br />\n<br />\n鬼鯊，一般外國人叫佢做「奇美拉」（音譯自Chimaera，直譯係混合獸，但因為奇美拉係一個種嘅統稱，同華文地區叫銀鮫一樣，所以下面統一叫返鬼鯊以正視聽），天生一副死魚眼﹑對鰭似翼，由於長居深海，基本上好少機會見過佢咃。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i3/rikDtH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi3%2FrikDtH.png&h=861e5c21&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n銀鮫同鯊魚﹑魔鬼魚同屬軟骨魚綱，但後兩者係板腮亞綱，魚腮睇落係一板一板，而且身體有鱗片；銀鮫係唯一一種全頭亞綱，你從旁觀察係見唔到佢副腮，而且身體冇鱗片。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i3/pI09Zd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi3%2FpI09Zd.png&h=42b148f2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上圖見到嘅鬼鯊係2009年發現嘅品種，據推算該品種應該已經存在咗差不多3億年，可以見到佢哋身上有化石級數嘅器官 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i3/JIR1HN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi3%2FJIR1HN.png&h=8e78b89f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n頭上面嘅一點點相信係獵物感測器，用嚟接收微弱嘅生命電磁波。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i3/MvVEo2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi3%2FMvVEo2.png&h=c7a22a67&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同一般銀鮫唔同，點鼻藍奇美拉比較喜歡多石嘅居住環境。 <br />\n<br />\n有關點鼻藍奇美拉資料，係由加洲水生研究所提供，該物種於2009年加洲至夏威夷一帶海域水深6,700呎附近發現。 <br />\n資料轉載自<a href=\"http://news.nationalgeographic.com/2016/12/pointy-nosed-blue-chimaeras-ghost-sharks/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.nationalgeographic.com%2F2016%2F12%2Fpointy-nosed-blue-chimaeras-ghost-sharks%2F&d=kZTSD3bhxdqFI9jV6RfYOmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=bd8f03f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.nationalgeographic.com/2016/12/pointy-nosed-blue-chimaeras-ghost-sharks/</a>"},{"pid":"bab3c33e5f2fc840997c2ef8c5783d3ed48f3fd6","tid":43463,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T14:39:23.000Z","msg":"留名等睇海綿寶寶張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe73404e8980c22693751de22c76dc6c5298ee3f","tid":43463,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:16:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c11de25e164ac7d6f00c865d3b6a379a1b5a872","tid":43463,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T03:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1d46a8921cdd8ba1910b6136ffa4a1110c6105","tid":43463,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T04:11:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d33d4879c2c0818aa0e845fb9d332cbfa9a9688","tid":43463,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:34:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bebb8a2f1cbebca540f6fcc1e24ade3d544fd04","tid":43463,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名等睇海綿寶寶張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c1c212ff5a732f56f129b54bc6011e2712cdc4b","tid":43463,"uid":6537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:55:14.000Z","msg":"thx樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p